parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rearview camera can cause a visibility hazard, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries when reversing.
symptoms: The rearview camera image is distorted
blank
or flickering; the camera fails to display an image; the "Rearview Camera Unavailable" message is displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Back Over Prevention system can cause a visibility hazard, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries when reversing.
symptoms: The backover prevention camera malfunctioned; the image was black or had a blue screen; the system failed to operate as needed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in receiving parts for the recall repair can cause a prolonged period of increased risk of accidents or injuries due to the faulty rearview camera or Back Over Prevention system.
symptoms: The part to do the recall repair was not yet available; the manufacturer had exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the trunk and locking system can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The trunk failed to open; the unlock button on the rear door
inside the vehicle
and on the key fob did not work; the rearview camera was displaying a blank image intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected unlatching of the passenger door while driving can cause the door to open, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the passenger is not wearing a seatbelt or is leaning against the door.
symptoms: The passenger door opens or becomes ajar while driving
often accompanied by a warning message on the dashboard
wind noise
and a sudden loss of pressure on the door.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected unlatching of the driver door while driving can cause the door to open, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the driver is not wearing a seatbelt or is leaning against the door.
symptoms: The driver door opens or becomes ajar while driving
often accompanied by a warning message on the dashboard
wind noise
and a sudden loss of pressure on the door.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected opening of the hood while driving can cause the hood to fly up and obstruct the driver's view, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The hood opens or becomes unlatched while driving
often accompanied by a loud noise and a sudden loss of visibility.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The chipping or bubbling of paint on the rear windshield or bumper can lead to rust and corrosion, potentially causing structural damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Paint chipping or bubbling on the rear windshield or bumper
often accompanied by rust or corrosion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The breakage of the bumper tabs can lead to reduced structural integrity of the bumper, potentially causing injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Broken or loose bumper tabs
often accompanied by a rattling or loose feeling on the bumper.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear view camera can cause a loss of visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rear view camera image is distorted
the camera screen goes black
the camera only works intermittently
or the camera does not work at all.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort, distraction, and visibility issues while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The air conditioning blows hot air
the air conditioning only works on low
or the air conditioning stops working altogether.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning of windows and door locks can cause inconvenience, distraction, and safety risks while driving.
symptoms: Windows roll up and down randomly
doors lock and unlock unexpectedly
or doors do not lock or unlock properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a loss of critical vehicle functions, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle's cluster panel or navigation screen goes blank
the vehicle's engine shuts off while driving
or the vehicle's electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heated/cooled seat system can cause discomfort, distraction, and potentially lead to a fire hazard.
symptoms: The heated/cooled seats malfunction
or the connector shows signs of burning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning of mirrors can cause visibility issues and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Mirrors pop or do not rotate properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distraction and inconvenience while driving.
symptoms: The infotainment screen fails to display properly
or Bluetooth connectivity issues occur.
